  <brief_title>A Study to Examine the Human Papillomavirus Types Exposure in Women From Southern Africa and Brasil</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Pilot Observational Study to Determine the Prevalence of HPV Serology in HIV Seropositive Women From Subsaharan Africa and Brasil</official_title>
